        {
            "title": "橋本環奈欺凌成癮第9位經理人離職 禍不單行晨早劇《御飯糰》收視插水",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"橋本環奈欺凌成癮第9位經理人離職 禍不單行晨早劇《御飯糰》收視插水\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5c6087983acbcb0c13edb11876d648f1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250220/_2025022015024183515.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">橋本環奈欺凌成癮第9位經理人離職 禍不單行晨早劇《御飯糰》收視插水</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>日本女星橋本環奈有「千年一遇美女」之稱，其晨早劇《御飯糰》於去年9月開播，首周平均收視有16.1%，但每況愈下，暫時全劇平均收視只有13.4%，刷新史上收視最低晨早劇，較2009年倉科加奈主演《歡迎龜來》的平均13.5%收視還要低，上檔的《虎翼》全劇平均收視則有16.8%。另外去年10月傳出橋本環奈「公主病」嚴重，嚇走8名經理人，近日再度傳出她涉職場欺凌，導致第9位經理人都離職，據悉原因是身心失調。\n\n</p><h2>橋本環奈又換經理人？</h2>\n<p>據日媒《週刊女性》報道，橋本環奈欺凌經理人並非新鮮事，只是經理人公司強烈否認。不過近日又有知情人爆料再有一位經理人疑因身心失調，在橋本環奈拍攝晨間劇《御飯糰》期間就已離職，該經理人表示在片場與橋本環奈零交流，因為對方的壓倒性的優勢，目前橋本環奈的經理人公司未就傳聞回應。橋本環奈身邊通常有3位經理人，一位是首席經理人，另外兩名則是會跟到片場的隨行經理人，她只對首席經理人態度良好，相反對隨行的經理人，就試過在片場痛斥他們，導致對方離職。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092564/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"橋本環奈再傳出欺凌經理人，導致第9位經理人離職。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/259c90afe54876ac4acb2c7d490516db/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_14_41_44.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        橋本環奈再傳出欺凌經理人，導致第9位經理人離職。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092565/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"橋本環奈主演的晨早劇《御飯糰》正在播放。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7aad961b7d2a0e43bb766bc90076da6b/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_14_41_45.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        橋本環奈主演的晨早劇《御飯糰》正在播放。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092566/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"橋本環奈主演的晨早劇《御飯糰》正在熱播，她飾演一位營養師。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb187d92e6bd92a08d958d773c7974fe/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_14_41_46_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        橋本環奈主演的晨早劇《御飯糰》正在熱播，她飾演一位營養師。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092567/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"橋本環奈主演的晨早劇《御飯糰》收視暫成晨早劇中最差。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/daabb1187677a8248c476dd0fed7a127/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_14_41_46_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        橋本環奈主演的晨早劇《御飯糰》收視暫成晨早劇中最差。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092568/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"近日再度傳出橋本環奈的負面消息。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b459977f56f7dc05268d6c7088e001be/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_14_41_46.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        近日再度傳出橋本環奈的負面消息。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092569/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"橋本環奈（左四）多次被指態度差，空穴來風必有因。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ea682d766716e18389939a4d00750dd6/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_14_41_47_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        橋本環奈（左四）多次被指態度差，空穴來風必有因。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092570/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"去年10月，橋本環奈已被傳態度差，激走8位經理人。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5e22c7609796074f4470f92cc50daa3b/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_14_41_47.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        去年10月，橋本環奈已被傳態度差，激走8位經理人。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
